I am so pleased to announce that my film One White Feather has been selected for best experimental short for @indieshortfest festival ARFF Berlin and Sunday Shorts festival, I hope you enjoy the trailer 🤍🦢

latestPosts.caption:
crimson leaf
angel wings
around the silver maple, snow falls in the distance 

once we lived by the river 
thunderstorms shook us to bones 
blood on the stones 
bread on the stove

that was so special, I loved spending the solstice with you thank you for coming down and being the most beautiful, kind and receptive listeners 🪽

latestPosts.caption:
“I used to think the saying “jack of all trades, master of none” was negative, but as I’ve kept going and creating more I’m like thank God I’m a jack of all trades. When you’re rushed or tight for money there’s nothing better than being able to do it yourself.” ⁠
⁠
@florenceros.e chatted to us about juggling different artistic mediums, making mistakes and embracing being a multi-faceted creative.⁠
